org.eclipse.papyrus.sysml14.requirements

Interface Satisfy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DirectedRelationshipPropertyPath, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Trace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SatisfyImpl

    public interface Satisfy
extends Trace
    A representation of the model object 'Satisfy'. A Satisfy relationship is a dependency between a requirement and a model element that fulfills the requirement. As with other dependencies, the arrow direction points from the satisfying (client) model element to the (supplier) requirement that is satisfied.
    See Also:
